schema.title: renderingRule
schema.description: Specifies the rendering rule for how the requested image should be rendered.

outputPixelType.description: the output pixel type defines the output image's pixel type.

rasterFunction.description: The raster function name identifies the processing or rendering to be performed. rasterFunctionArguments.description: The arguments for the referenced `rasterFunction`. variableName.description: Variable name for the raster function.
